		title: "Developing Node.js Applications on IBM Bluemix",
		authors: ["Ahmed Azraq", "Mohamed Ewies", "Ahmed E. Marzouk"],
		description:
			"<span><p>Abstract</p><p>This IBM® Redbooks® publication explains how to create various\napplications based on Node.js and run them on IBM Bluemix®. In this\nbook, you will do the following activities:<br/></p><br/><li><p/><p>Develop a Hello World application in Node.js, executing on IBM\nBluemix. Through this activity, you can learn about these\ntechnologies:<br/></p><br/></li><li><p>IBM SDK for Node.js<br/></p></li><li><p>Eclipse Orion Web IDE<br/></p></li><li><p>Use asynchronous callback<br/></p></li><li><p>Create an Express application<br/></p></li><li><p>Build a rich user interface application by using AngularJS based\nin Node.js<br/></p></li><p><br/>\nThis book is for beginner and experienced developers who want to\nstart coding Node.js applications on IBM Bluemix.</p></span>",
